.Dd Dec 26, 2005
.Dt SETUP.WEBLOG 8
.Os MASTODON
.Sh NAME
.Nm setup.weblog
.Nd Set up an Annotations weblog for a user
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm setup.weblog
.Op Ar User
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm Setup.weblog
sets up a weblog for a user, generating required directories, building
the cgi shellscripts needed for posting, editing, and commenting,
asking for the admin password, then generating the pages.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr weblog.conf 5 ,
.Xr annotations 7 ,
.Xr @EXEC_PREFIX@reindex 8
